{"query": "Please take this CSV information on an individual and do some analysis.  Specifically, I would like you to tell me some generalizations about the people that this person's company work with.  I would like to develop an Ideal Customer Profile for this person.  Please give me a summary of the people who are most likely to do business with this organization.

Please be as specific as possible in terms of job titles, locations, company size, and revenue range.

Please look up relevant industries and use their ID based on the INDUSTRY DATA JSON object.

As this profile will be fed into our software, I would like you to format a JSON object with the following example format for the ICP: 

{
    "contact_email_status":["verified"],
    "per_page":25,
    "page":1,
    "person_titles":["ceo","president"],
    "person_locations":["Dallas, Texas", "United States"],
    "organization_industry_tag_ids":["5567ce5b73696439a17a0000","5567cd477369645401010000"],
    "organization_num_employees_ranges":["1,10","11,20","21,50","51,100"],
    "revenue_range":{"max":"10000000","min":"1000000"}
}
